text: Great food! Top notch service. Awesome hospitality! This neighbourhood bar is just awesome!

Nestled in a charming rustic setting, this  bistro offers a delightful escape from the ordinary. Savor the essence of the countryside as you indulge in their selection of finger foods, expertly paired with a diverse range of wines and beers. The warm ambiance and the enticing menu make it the perfect retreat for those seeking a casual yet a refined experience.

I walked in to shelter from the rain. Met Martin our host and had great wine, beer and food.
Amazing.
Non Pretentious drinking wall.. Great Prices and very cozy ambience!!!
